{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[10422,1420],"id":"805572ea-a61c-4a8c-ac2f-ffa5bd6bdd17","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Contact Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Company, Dealstage). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Contact","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"16796ed8-60b3-75ee-f200-fdd907f5cc61","name":"Note: New Contact Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Contact\n\nShapes the item: writes `contactId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"4f66f7ee-bbbb-dda1-92f1-fd3b4473f450","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Contact"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.contactId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Score the Lead · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"4d076138-5abc-18de-7aa6-97c8bbd4af06","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nCreates or updates a HubSpot contact by email — HubSpot is the CRM system of record for this pipeline.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"94e86da3-aa9b-2003-5323-515f41bdf871","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score the Lead\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each contact 0-100 from simple heuristics\